    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 12.84,
      "end": 16.18,
      "text": "Recorded by Lee Dunkelberg, Dunkelberg.com.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 16.46,
      "end": 19.6,
      "text": "Do you end K-E-L-B-E-R-G dot com.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 20.86,
      "end": 24.24,
      "text": "Esop's fables, the rich man and the Tanner.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 25.18,
      "end": 29.76,
      "text": "Our rich man took up his residence next door to a Tanner,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 30.44,
      "end": 36.84,
      "text": "and found the smell of the tan yard so extremely unpleasant",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 36.84,
      "end": 40.52,
      "text": "that he told him he must go.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 41.54,
      "end": 46.04,
      "text": "The Tanner delayed his departure, and the rich man had to speak",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 46.04,
      "end": 47.58,
      "text": "to him several times about it.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 48.22,
      "end": 51.5,
      "text": "And every time the Tanner said he was making arrangements",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 51.5,
      "end": 52.88,
      "text": "to move very shortly.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 54.14,
      "end": 56.4,
      "text": "This went on for some time.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 57.5,
      "end": 66.92,
      "text": "Till at last, the rich man got so used to the smell that he ceased to mind it,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-015",
      "start": 67.66,
      "end": 71.24,
      "text": "and troubled the Tanner with his objections, no more.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-016",
      "start": 72.74,
      "end": 75.64,
      "text": "End of the rich man and the Tanner.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
